lead_paragraph: Twice champion Victoria Azarenka schooled Japanese teenager Naomi Osaka 6-1 6-1 to reach the fourth round of the Australian Open on Saturday and issue an ominous statement to her rivals.

headline.print_headline: Azarenka Hammers Qualifier Osaka to Reach Fourth Round
